    description:
      "Have a project you're struggling with? I can help you unblock.",
  },
];
---

<Layout 
  title="Tutoring"
  themeColorLight="#ddd6fe"
  themeColorDark="#581c87"
>
  <DefaultPage theme="tutoring">
    <Container>
      <h1
        class="font-sanstight mb-4 text-5xl leading-none font-bold md:text-6xl"
      >
        Expert tutoring in mathematics and computer science.
      </h1>

      <section
        class="mb-16 flex flex-col flex-wrap items-center md:items-start gap-y-4 text-xl sm:flex-col md:flex-row md:gap-x-4"
      >
        <Button
          variant="primary"
          background="#3b82f6"
          href="mailto:tutoring@login.blubits.me"
        >
          Send me an email
        </Button>
        <Button
          variant="secondary"
          href="https://www.teacheron.com/tutor/67qr"
        >
          Go to TeacherOn
        </Button>
      </section>
    </Container>

    <Container class="mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">What I tutor</h2>
    </Container>

    <CardContainer height="h-116">
      <Fragment slot="cards">
        {
          cardData.map((card) => (
            <CardItem
              title={card.title}
              description={card.description}
              customHeight="h-108"
            >
              <CardThumbIcon slot="thumbnail" emoji={card.emoji} bg_color="bg-gradient-to-tr from-blue-600 via-blue-500 to-blue-400" />
            </CardItem>
          ))
        }
      </Fragment>
    </CardContainer>

    <Container class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-4 gap-x-4 gap-y-8 md:grid-cols-12">
      <div class="col-span-4 max-w-prose md:col-span-12">
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-3xl font-semibold">Proven expertise.</h2>
        <p class="max-w-prose leading-normal">
          I've been a computer science tutor for 7 years and a programmer for
          over a decade. As a summa cum laude graduate in computer science and a
          competitor in various programming competitions, I have a deep
          understanding of algorithms, data structures, mathematics, and
          computer science in general.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-4 max-w-prose md:col-span-5">
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-semibold">
          Delivering teaching that works.
        </h2>
        <p class="max-w-prose leading-normal">
          When you get me as a tutor, you get results. My students have gone on
          to pass and excel in their exams, succeed in their classes, and even win competitions. We'll work together to achieve the results you want.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-4 max-w-prose md:col-span-5 md:col-end-12">
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-semibold">Tailored for you.</h2>
        <p class="max-w-prose leading-normal">
          My teaching style fits your needs and learning style. I focus on
          breaking down topics into concepts that you understand. I emphasize
          practice and application so you see the big picture. And we'll go at a
          pace that you're comfortable with.
        </p>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </DefaultPage>
</Layout>
